<h4>Root Causes</h4>

<ol><li>Event listeners not being properly reinitialized after page navigation</li></ol>

<ol><li>CSS color variables not properly following the site's theme</li></ol>

<ol><li>Duplicate and conflicting CSS/JS files</li></ol>

<ol><li>Submenu positioning issues on different screen sizes</li></ol>

<ol><li>Improper HTML structure in admintopmenu.tt</li></ol>



<h4>Changes Made</h4>

<ol><li>Fixed HTML structure in admintopmenu.tt to ensure proper nesting</li></ol>

<ol><li>Updated admintopmenu.tt to use the standard menu.css and menu.js files</li></ol>

<ol><li>Eliminated code duplication and conflicts</li></ol>

<ol><li>Enhanced menu.css with improved styling</li></ol>

